title: An update from Jennifer that was on Group Therapy yesterday
description:
Jennifer was on Group Therapy yesterday telling us she met a guy on a recent flight and fell for him hard. 
 Now she's thinking about ending things with her fiance that she's been with for a while.  We check-in with her today to see if she made a decision about what she's going to do.
